&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain detailed records of all assembly and testing processes, ensuring accuracy and attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to read and meticulously follow engineering drawings and assembly procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable and attentive while working hands-on with tools such as a Dremel, soldering iron, and crimpers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;US citizenship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Local to the Bay Area, commuting to Hayward office required (CA)&lt;/li&gt;
